comments: Williamson (NOP) establishes himself in a screening position in Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) path and does not deliver the contact.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) initiates contact with Ingram's (NOP) right arm as he ends his drive and starts his upward shooting motion.
Favors (NOP) briefly has his hands on Porzingis' (DAL) near hip before correcting.
Porzingis (DAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Ball's (NOP) path and does not deliver the contact.
Kleber (DAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Holiday's (NOP) path and does not deliver the contact.
Ingrim (NOP) places a hand to Kelber's (DAL) side and does not affect his SQBR.
Williamson (NOP) establishes a screening behind Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) without initiating contact. Hardaway Jr. then turns off the screen to pursue Ingram.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) extends his hand against Ingram's (NOP) side as he defends him over the pick without grabbing his uniform or affecting his SQBR.
Porzingis (DAL) fails to fully clear or guard an opponent within three seconds after entering the lane.
Kleber (DAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Ball's (NOP) path and does not deliver the contact.
Holiday (NOP) makes contact with the ball and dislodges it from Kleber's (DAL) control before making additional incidental contact.
Favors (NOP) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it from Hardaway Jr. (DAL) as they each attempt to gain control of the rebound.
Favors (NOP) puts a legal hand against Doncic's (DAL) side as he drives and Doncic brings his arm back as he is running, making contact with his arm and then passing.
Williamson (NOP) and Kleber (DAL) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) and Ingram (NOP) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Favors (NOP) establishes himself in a screening position in Curry's (DAL) path and does not deliver the contact.
Curry (DAL) briefly grasps and releases Favors' (NOP) shorts as Favors begins rolling toward the lane.
Favors (NOP) establishes his right foot as his pivot after gaining control of the rebound, and legally lifts it off of the floor to pass the ball, which he does before re-planting it.

Porzingis (DAL) briefly clasps and releases Favors' (NOP) arm during the missed shot attempt, but does not affect Favors' ability to retrieve the rebound. The ball does not hit the rim and the shot clock correctly continues to count down without resetting to 14 seconds.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) makes marginal contact with a hand to Ingram (NOP) without affecting his SQBR. Ingram brings the ball up and over without any arm contact and fumbles the ball and then recovers.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) maintains a legal forearm to Ingram (NOP) as he drives.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) briefly has his hands to Ingram's (NOP) sides from behind without delaying him when he disengages.
Ingram (NOP) commits the take foul on Curry (DAL).
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) commits the take foul on Ingram (NOP).

Porzingis (DAL) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Melli (NOP) after the release of his jump shot attempt. After communicating with the Replay Center, it was determined both of Melli's feet were behind the three point line.
Porzingis (DAL) and Ingram (NOP) engage and disengage before the inbound.
Holiday (NOP) and Doncic (DAL) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Ingram (NOP) place a legal hand against Porzingis (DAL) during his drive without affecting his SQBR.
Porzingis (DAL) stops with his arm bent against Ingram (NOP) and releases when he steps back to set for the jump shot.
Ingram (NOP) legally contests Porzingis' (DAL) jump shot attempt.
Doncic (DAL) makes marginal contact with Favors' (NOP) backside during rebounding.
Ingram (NOP) initiates contact with his hand and body to Porzingis' (DAL) upper half at the start of his drive.
Ball (NOP) moves into Doncic's (DAL) space and initiates contact to Doncic's lower half at the end of the drive.
Williamson (NOP) avoids bringing both hands to the ball as he dribbles along the lane line.
Kleber (DAL) maintains legal guarding position as body contact occurs with Williamson (NOP) during his upward shooting motion.
Porzingis (DAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Ball's (NOP) path and does not deliver the contact, some of which occurs to Ball's side.
Williamson (NOP) drives low and goes to, but not through, Kleber (DAL), who initially steps wide and to his right to get ahead of Williamson, and then turns.
Kleber (DAL) continues to lean over Williamson (NOP) as he drives, with his arms and torso out over Williamson as he comes up to take the shot.
Ball (NOP) makes marginal contact with his forearm to Doncic's (DAL) front near half-court.
Porzingis (DAL) is firming up on his left leg prior to contact occurring with Ball (NOP) during the pick.
Favors (NOP) makes marginal contact with Porzingis' (DAL) arm during the successful dunk.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position with his body during Holiday's (NOP) drives and makes marginal contact with his hand against his body that does not affect his SQBR.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Holiday's (NOP) path and does not deliver the contact.
Holiday (NOP) maintains a legal guarding position with his body at the start of Doncic's (DAL) drives, and makes marginal contact with his hand that does not affect his SQBR.
Doncic (DAL) stops short and releases contact from Holiday (NOP) without pushing off.
Ball (NOP) and Doncic (DAL) engages before Doncic disengages and taps the ball out to Hardaway Jr. (DAL).
Williamson (NOP) commits the take foul on Hardaway Jr. (DAL).
Kleber (DAL) makes marginal contact with Williamson's (NOP) left side during his driving shot attempt.
Hart (NOP) and Hardaway Jr. (DAL) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Kleber (DAL) and Holiday (NOP) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Melli (NOP) commits the take foul on Porzingis (DAL).
Kleber (DAL) removes his resting hand off Holiday's (NOP) body prior to his upward shooting motion.
Doncic (DAL) and Williamson (NOP) make incidental arm contact with another before Doncic cleanly dislodges the ball thereafter.
Jackson (NOP) makes incidental foot contact with the ball as it is loose during rebounding.
